  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Explore the hidden gems of Europe in comfort, style, and without breaking your stride. An easy walking holiday is perfect for those seeking a leisurely and low-impact way to explore. The walks are designed to be relaxing and enriching, providing an opportunity to soak in the local culture and stunning landscapes. You’ll get to stroll along picturesque trails that offer gentle slopes and easy terrain, making it a comfortable experience for travelers of all ages and fitness levels. </span></p>
<p><strong>Browse our recommended resorts for easy walking:</strong></p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Italy" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Italy">Resort 1</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Austria" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Austria">Resort 2</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Switzerland" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Switzerland">Resort 3</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Slovenia" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Slovenia">Resort 4</a> </h3>
<p><span><img src="/media/13093605/easy-walking-hero-838x450.jpg" alt="Easy Walking" data-udi="umb://media/ca07af4dabf1446e99471194c518c210" /></span></p>
<h2>What to expect from our easy walking holidays</h2>
<p>We offer easy walks through Europe's most beautiful destinations, where you can explore the local culture and make your own discoveries. </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>What is an easy walking holiday?</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%px; height: autopx;" src="/media/13093530/close-up-feet.png?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ada05f0bc8de4c3d84cb81a1965dba1d" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Flatter trails and easy terrain with places to take in the view. </span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Shorter walks are available and can be accessed straight from the piste from the town or via transport and lifts to viewpoints. </span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Free guided walks in selected resorts included</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%px; height: auto;" src="/media/13093531/close-up-walking.png?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6a1275fcf4c849cc870dc70996b0952e" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">We offer free guided walks in selected resorts, run by local experts. </span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">We'll guide you through some of the best parts of each location with insider tips and tricks. </span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Our self-guided walking holidays offer total flexibility</h3>
<p><img style="width: autopx; height: 100%;" src="/media/13080490/merano-tourist-board-image-8.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ddef516ea88a4726b9a4ac183045b915" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">You'll be free to explore on your own terms and experience the culture, cuisine and sights. </span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">You'll have the support of our resort representatives to offer advice and tips if you need it. </span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Discover our most popular resorts for easy walking holidays</h2>
<p>Our easy walks are perfect for all abilities, and there’s something for everyone. Whether your focus is the stunning Italian Lakes or Austrian Mountains, there’s endless walking destinations available to explore - from the effortlessly scenic to off-the-beaten track adventures that offer even greater reward. </p>
